folder: Judge Street & Whitney Avenue, Queens, NY
text:
Judge Street, north side, from Whitney Avenue (left) to 43rd Avenue, showing St. Bartholomews Roman Catholic School. The two views are north across the triangular Elmhurst Memorial Park. The later photograph shows also the steeple of the new St. Bartholomews Church, on Ithaca Street. The church property is bounded by Whitney and 43rd Avenues and Judge and Ithaca Streets.

P. L. Sperr
View 1: June 7, 1927
View 2: April 25, 1936
